summary:
Animation Bash of multiple animation mods in one with idea of female in mind only.Hint use with Female's facial and body animation.
This is a Animation Compilation meant for female user's.

The femaleheadbrows.tri is a facial animation used for female faces to make them more femine instead of the vanilla facial animation.
